# Exercises

1. A teacher wants to know what percentage of men and what percentage of women are in a group of students.

2. A student wants to know what his final grade in the subject of Algorithms will be. This rating consists of the following percentages:

    * 55% is the average of his three partial grades.
    * 30% is the final exam grade.
    * 15% is the final work grade.

3.  In a hospital there are three areas: Gynecology, Pediatrics and Traumatology. The annual budget of the hospital is distributed according to the following table:

    * Gynecology 40%
    * Traumatology 30%
    * Pediatrics 30%

    Obtain the amount of money that each area will receive, for any budget.
